        "text_fPWJfk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h1></h1><p>At MINDYES, we believe that quality and peace of mind are essential parts of every outdoor living experience. That’s why we stand behind our products with a reliable warranty and responsive customer support.</p><p></p><p></p><h2><strong>3-Year Limited Warranty</strong></h2><p>All MINDYES products are covered by a <strong>3-year limited warranty</strong> from the date of delivery. This warranty covers defects in materials and workmanship under normal residential use.</p><p></p><p></p><h3><strong>What Is Covered</strong></h3><p>This warranty includes protection against manufacturing defects in the following areas:</p><h4><strong>Structural Components</strong></h4><p>· Frame deformation or structural failure under normal use </p><p>· Cracking or warping caused by manufacturing defects </p><h4><strong>Functional Parts</strong></h4><p>· Hardware components and fittings </p><p>· Mechanical moving parts (if applicable) </p><p>· Product-integrated systems designed for normal operation </p><h4><strong>Material Defects</strong></h4><p>· Manufacturing-related defects in materials or finishes </p><p>· Failure not caused by external damage or misuse </p><p></p><p></p><h2><strong>What Is Not Covered</strong></h2><p>This warranty does not cover:</p><p>· Damage caused by improper installation or assembly </p><p>· Misuse, abuse, or neglect of the product </p><p>· Accidental damage or external impact </p><p>· Modifications or unauthorized repairs </p><p>· Normal wear and tear over time </p><p>· Damage caused by weather extremes beyond product specifications </p><p></p><p></p><h2><strong>Warranty Service</strong></h2><p>If a covered issue occurs within the warranty period, we will provide one of the following solutions based on the situation:</p><p>· Replacement of defective parts </p><p>· Repair guidance or technical support </p><p>· Partial or full replacement (depending on severity) </p><p>All warranty decisions are made after inspection of the issue.</p><p></p><p></p><h2><strong>Replacement Parts for Non-Covered Issues</strong></h2><p>If damage is not covered under warranty (for example, user-caused damage), we still provide support and replacement parts at a reasonable cost. Please contact us for assistance.</p><p></p><p></p><h2><strong>How to Submit a Warranty Claim</strong></h2><p>To request warranty support, please contact us at:</p><p>Email: support@mindyes.com</p><p>Please include:</p><p>· Order number or proof of purchase </p><p>· Description of the issue </p><p>· Clear photos or videos (if applicable) </p><p>Our support team will respond within <strong>24–48 hours</strong> and guide you through the next steps.</p><p></p><p></p><h2><strong>Support Commitment</strong></h2><p>At MINDYES, our commitment does not end after delivery. We aim to provide long-term product support and a smooth ownership experience.</p><p>Whether it’s installation guidance, replacement parts, or product questions, our team is here to help ensure your outdoor space remains functional, reliable, and enjoyable.</p><p> </p>"
